rows.label: qst202107_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, Shiki,
d'you think it might be time to go?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0002
rows.name: I think we've done enough.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0003
rows.name: Shiki, should we head back?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0004
rows.name: You've been at it for a while.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0005
rows.name:
Shiki, don't you think we should
be heading back soon?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0006
rows.name:
This is not a good place to
tarry in too long.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0007
rows.name: Hey, Shiki. Let's head back soon.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0008
rows.name: Don't you think you've done enough?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0009
rows.name:
What are you saying?!
I've got no intention of moving.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0010
rows.name:
If you want to go back, then
by all means, be my guest.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0011
rows.name: I'll just live here from now on.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0012
rows.name: Don't be ridiculous!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0013
rows.name: We've got stuff to do still!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0014
rows.name: No way, girl.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0015
rows.name: We've still got bigger fish to fry.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0016
rows.name: I cannot in good faith authorize that.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0017
rows.name:
There are other matters we must
all attend to.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0018
rows.name:
No, come on. There's no way
you're doing that.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0019
rows.name: We've got loads to take care of.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0020
rows.name:
But I don't want to!
I don't want to be anywhere else!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0021
rows.name:
If I don't research this place,
who do you think will?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0022
rows.name:
This is of vital importance to
everyone on Alst!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0023
rows.name:
I give up...
I can see you're resolved.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0024
rows.name:
Fine, you can keep investigating
until you're happy.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0025
rows.name:
I can't deal with this.
I can see you won't budge...

rows.label: qst202107_msg0026
rows.name:
Go ahead then, study it as much
as you want.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0027
rows.name: Your will really is indomitable, Shiki.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0028
rows.name:
I'll acquiesce.
You can study this place to your
heart's content.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0029
rows.name:
Yeah, yeah, okay.
You win, Shiki.

rows.label: qst202107_msg0030
rows.name:
You can keep up your investigation
or what have you. Just come help us
out sometime too, okay?

rows.label: qst202107_msg0031
rows.name: Awesome!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0032
rows.name: Thanks, Driver dearest!

rows.label: qst202107_msg0033
rows.name:
I just love understanding,
and I'm glad we've reached one!
